{"word":"ὦκα","slug":"ὦκα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὦκα</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:poetically'>poet.</a> <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> of <a href='S:ὠκύς'><el>ὠκύς</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>quickly, swiftly, fast</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>; <a href='S:strengthened'>strengthd.</a>, <el>μάλ' ὦκα, ὦκα μάλ'</el> <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of Time, <el>ὦκα ἔπειτα</el> <i>immediately</i> thereafter, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}